name: ConvertFahrenheittoCelsius
0:
”Alexa, open Fahrenheit Celsius”
”Alexa, open Fahrenheit Celsius and convert 50 Fahrenheit”
”Alexa, open Fahrenheit Celsius and 50 Fahrenheit”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: fahrenheit celsius
des:
This skill converts a Fahrenheit value to its corresponding Celsius value.
When prompted for the Fahrenheit say the Fahrenheit value. This can be any positive number.
The skill will respond with the corresponding Celsius value.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
